      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TODD KEEPING (2) finished in the minors last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 400m at this track, taking a Grade 4/5 in a dazzling 22.35. Rates on top and can find winning form again. DAKOTA RYLEN (1) recorded two placings in a row before an overdue win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths (30.82) at Angle Park. Should be in this for a long way. DAKOTA AVA (6) ran below best last time finishing fourth (19.66) over 342m at Angle Park in a Grade 4/5. Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Speedy beginner who can find the front despite the tricky draw. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. SHE'S A JUMBO (4) is in the mix after placing at a big quote last time out.",
